snippet.title: SSX 3 - All Peak Run (Part 1)
snippet.description:
Just a nostalgic nod back to one of my first videos where I played SSX 3.

My attempt to get down the whole mountain in under 22 mins (length of 2 youtube videos).

Bought the game again (this time for gamecube) and played it again to record this =)

Download: http://crankeye.net/media/video/roph/youtube/raws/SSX_3_-_All_Peak_Run__Part_1_.mp4
